Download the necessary wheels by executing in src/blentom:

python -m pip download ase pymcubes --dest .\blentom\wheels\ --only-binary=:all: --python-version=3.11 --platform=win_amd64
python -m pip download ase pymcubes --dest .\blentom\wheels\ --only-binary=:all: --python-version=3.11 --platform=macosx_12_0_arm64
python -m pip download ase pymcubes --dest .\blentom\wheels\ --only-binary=:all: --python-version=3.11 --platform=manylinux2014_x86_64

Build with:
make all